<p style="text-align: justify;">Uruguay is only the country with the title of first FIFA World Cup winner in 1930 and also the first hosting country of FIFA World Cup. With 12 appearances in FIFA World Cup Uruguay has managed to win it twice. In 1950 Uruguay won FIFA World Cup for the second time against the hosting country <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/brazil-road-russia-fifa-world-cup-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Brazil</a>. The football association in Uruguay was formed in 1900.The goalscorer of final in 1930 for Uruguay was Pablo Dorado in the 12<sup>th</sup> minute, Pedro Cea on the 57<sup>th</sup> minute, Santos Iriarte on the 68<sup>th</sup> minute and Hector Castro on the 89<sup>th</sup> minute of the game. However, <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/argentina-russia-world-cup-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Argentina</a> managed to score twice on 20<sup>th</sup> and 37<sup>th</sup> minute of the final and defeated against Uruguay. Uruguay has qualified for FIFA World Cup 2018 to <a href="http://wikiceleb.com/russia-host-fifa-world-cup-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Russia</a>.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-393" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Uruguay_goal_v_argentina_1930-300x197.jpg" alt="" width="630" height="414" />
